63.4	Strategy_of_tension	Strategy of tension	The strategy of tension (Italian: ) is a theory that describes how to divide, manipulate, and control public opinion using fear, propaganda, disinformation, psychological warfare, agents provocateurs, and false flag terrorist actions.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/41/Stragedibologna-2.jpg/250px-Stragedibologna-2.jpg
